               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist, names of the donor and other persons; groups of lines on the incipit page; incipit of all sections; incipit or the initial word of subsections; the word sälam "salutation"; the word bä-ʾǝntä "about" on fol. 62ra; elements of the punctuation signs and of the text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="coloph1">
                     <colophon>
                        <locus target="92vb"/>Fol. 92vb: ተፈጸመ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ በእደ፡ ጸሐፌሁ፡ ቄስ፡ ደስታ፡ ገ/ማርያም፡ ዘብሔረ፡ ልጋት፡ በ፲ወ፱፻፷ወ፭ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት። ወተሣየጦ፡ በ፹ወ፭ብሩር፡ [vac.] ወወሀቦ፡ ለታቦተ፡ ማርያም፡ ዓዲ፡ ቀያሕቶ። ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጲጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡ ወአሜን፡ ለይኩን፡ ለይኩን።<foreign xml:lang="en">This book was completed by the hand of the scribe priest Dästa Gäbrä Maryam from the land of Lǝgat in the year of mercy 1965. [vac.] He has purchased it for 85 Bǝrr and donated it to the church of Mary ʿAddi Qiyaḥto. The one who stole it or erased (its text) shall be excommunicated by the authority of Peter and Paul. For ever and ever. Amen and amen. Let it be, let it be.</foreign>
                        <note>The year of mercy 1965 corresponds to 1972/73 A.D. The space for the name of the commissioner has been left unfilled (?).</note>
                     </colophon>
                  </msItem>
