                        <persName role="scribe" corresp="PRS00000">Dästa Gäbrä Maryam</persName>Priest Dästa Gäbrä Maryam from Lǝgat is mentioned as the scribe in the colophon. He is the same scribe who wrote Mss. FBM-012 and UM-008.<date>20th century</date>
